verbose_text: Kim et al. reported that AGM TRIM5alpha derived from Chlorocebus tantalus but not Chlorocebus pygerythrus subspecies of AGM restrict SIVmac239, while both potently restrict HIV-1.
evidence: AGM TRIM5alpha derived from Chlorocebus tantalus but not Chlorocebus pygerythrus subspecies of AGM restrict SIVmac239
